const SimpleTreeMap = ({ height, width }) => {
    return (
        <RechartCreator height={height} width={width}>
            <Treemap
                isAnimationActive={true}
                data={data}
                dataKey="size"
                ratio={4 / 3}
                stroke="#fff"
                fill="#8884d8"
            />
        </RechartCreator>
    )
}

export default SimpleTreeMap
